*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Include          ZBK_P004_F01
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*

*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form form1
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM form1 .
DATA: lv_num2 TYPE int4.
gv_num1 = gv_num1 + 1.
lv_num2 = lv_num2 + 1.
ENDFORM.

*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form form2
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM form2 .
gv_num1 = gv_num1 + 1.
*lv_num2 = lv_num2 + 1.
ENDFORM.